<p>These examples represent a range of stake pool operators, from large to smaller pools, showing how they contribute to load balancing and decentralization in the Cardano ecosystem. The figures for stake delegated are approximations and can vary over time. The classification of their contribution to load balancing (high, medium, low) is also indicative, based on their relative size and influence in the network.</p>



