<li><strong>Ouroboros Protocol Optimization</strong>: Cardano&#8217;s underlying consensus mechanism, Ouroboros, must continually evolve to support greater scalability while maintaining decentralization and security.</li>



<li><strong>Layer-2 Scaling Protocols:</strong> Implementing technologies like Hydra and state channels can offload transaction processing from the main chain, providing scalability enhancements without compromising the base layer&#8217;s integrity.</li>
</ol>



